WEBVTT

00:00,000 --> 00:02,950
A practical leadership workflow for data and analytics that teams will use 03040530 sounds strategic, but the real constraint is operating behavior in the workflow.

00:03,000 --> 00:05,950
As output scales, decision clarity becomes the real bottleneck. Last week in the weekly operations standup, the blocker was not motivation.

00:06,000 --> 00:08,950
Problem one: teams collect more inputs, but weak checkpoints keep outcomes flat.

00:09,000 --> 00:11,950
Then convert one recurring meeting into a decision checkpoint with explicit next actions.

00:12,000 --> 00:14,950
Then launch a refined version inside one focused week, not after a long cycle.

00:15,000 --> 00:17,950
Problem two: teams drift when analytics expectations change faster than coaching adapts.

00:18,000 --> 00:20,950
So the strategic question is whether the system improves decisions or only produces artifacts.

00:21,000 --> 00:29,950
What do you think?
